#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/ronl-business-api%5Cdeveloper%5Cdeployment%5Cpostgresql.md:3
msgid ""
"The RONL Business API uses **Azure PostgreSQL Flexible Server** as its "
"persistent store for audit logs. The database is provisioned per environment "
"— `ronl-postgres-acc` for ACC and `ronl-postgres-prod` for production — and "
"is accessed exclusively by the backend running on Azure App Service."
msgstr ""

